{"tid":1361902,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【集中討論】7.27 元朗遊行 文宣、物資、行動組請入內商討行動細節","createTime":"2019-07-24T17:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T05:06:51.000Z","uid":220645,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8fa09011c3c25fdec295632ecb5b54f242527005","tid":1361902,"uid":220645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:03:05.000Z","msg":"距離星期六只係得返三日，準備時間其實已經好短，所以希望各位實事派人士能夠快速準確咁定下可能係有史而嚟最危險嘅遊行的細節。以下係我嘅一啲建議，希望大家討論吓有咩要做/改同快速達成共識及行動<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能有啲位有問題，希望大家能指出，加上你嘅意見同盡快達成共識，謝謝<br />\n(先set個deadline喺星期四下午四點)"},{"pid":"bec75109708da9b9ba59f56911afcb55c88e734c","tid":1361902,"uid":220645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:03:51.000Z","msg":"時日無多，求意見"},{"pid":"695e989d3f0fdea63d1d58ec9a3024e837ef7cf3","tid":1361902,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:04:02.000Z","msg":"元朗手足有野講 727去唔去都入黎睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"69e549358f3b008a785969a5a5f7f176fa7e5bfc","tid":1361902,"uid":220645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:04:22.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"3a592151a1b18b74fed8918f088e2cf20b313822","tid":1361902,"uid":220645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:05:25.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"d775092bae009bada41cd6632e25b97b666b2b0a","tid":1361902,"uid":220645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:06:09.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"4e02f81e12a69536f1c3e10f560312f18f7a748c","tid":1361902,"uid":220645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:06:35.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"0b0fac6c4a716e34072598ef08927b098c2598de","tid":1361902,"uid":220645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:06:56.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"45040f94ed